title: Pinocchio, Vampire Slayer Vol.03 - Of Wood and Blood TPB (2014)
description:
Pinocchio, Vampire Slayer Vol.03 - Of Wood and Blood TPB (2014) (digital-Empire)


After being left for dead, adrift in the middle of the Mediterranean, Pinocchio and what remains of the Great Puppet Theater wash ashore on a mysterious island. But before they can resume their efforts to save Carlotta from the vampires, they must first survive the deadly Vrykolakas. This is the collected Pinocchio, Vampire Slayer: Of Wood and Blood #01-06 the final chapter in the critically acclaimed trilogy!
